title: Waitrose supports Cullercoats Lifeboat during October (RNLI - Royal National Lifeboat Institution)
text: ( Source : RNLI - Royal National Lifeboat Institution ) Lifeboats News Release Date : 17/10/ 2015 Author : Michael Scott Shoppers at Waitrose store in Eldon Square have the opportunity to help raise funds for the Lifeboat Station at Cullercoats .
